---
---
<section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Full stack developer · Curitiba, BR</p>
    <h1>Building products people<br />actually enjoy using.</h1>
    <p class="bio">
        I design and build web applications end-to-end — from architecture to
        pixel-perfect interfaces. I also write about what I learn along the way.
    </p>
    <div class="btns">
        <a href="/#projects" class="btn-primary">View projects</a>
        <a href="/blog" class="btn-secondary">Read the blog</a>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .hero {
        padding: 56px 0 44px;
        border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    }
    .eyebrow {
        font-size: 11px;
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--teal-400);
        margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    h1 {
        font-size: 36px;
        font-weight: 500;
        line-height: 1.2;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .bio {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        max-width: 500px;
        margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .btns {
        display: flex;
        gap: 10px;
    }
    .btn-primary {
        background: var(--teal-600);
        color: var(--teal-50);
        padding: 10px 22px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 500;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
        background: var(--teal-800);
        color: var(--teal-50);
    }
    .btn-secondary {
        background: transparent;
        color: var(--teal-600);
        border: 0.5px solid var(--teal-100);
        padding: 10px 22px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 13px;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover {
        background: var(--teal-50);
    }
</style>
